reviewText: Excellent seller and excellent product; no complaints at all.

I was so happy to  find "The Piano Lesson" I did not read the info. If I had, I would seen that it was "VHS"! I do not want to return it, as.. I do have  a VHS player. I  wish to thank the seller and I am grateful for their input. The item was as they said and I look forward to dealing with them in the future!! Thank you. @InfiniteMinds)
